description: Unbeatable price! Discover the pinnacle of luxury resort-style living at EchelonSeaport. This exceptional 17th-floor southeast-facing corner residence boasts unobstructed views of the Atlantic Ocean. With two bedrooms, two baths, and two valet garage parking spaces, this home features custom flooring, automatic window treatments, bespoke closets, and enhanced lighting. Highly sought-after during presales for its spacious layout and prime location, this residence stands out for elegance and comfort. Residents enjoy unparalleled amenities, including three pools, a hot tub and spa, a sports court with pickleball, a fitness center, sports simulator, and Pilates studio. The Club Level offers a fireplace lounge, private dining, and outdoor terraces with grill stations and firepits, all designed to extend your living space. Additional services include 24/7 concierge, doorman, and porters, ensuring a seamless living experience.
